## Future Scope

Healthcare robotics continues to evolve through AI, machine learning, IoT, cloud computing, and advanced sensor technologies. Future developments include autonomous surgical assistants, intelligent rehabilitation systems, soft robotics, brain-controlled prosthetics, and nanorobotics for targeted drug delivery, enabling safer, more personalized, and more accessible healthcare.

